{"type": "article", "id": 17568, "title": "19 条捷径，条条通往设计感丨好奇心研究所", "description": "随便看看，都是充分不必要条件。", "date": "2015-11-15T07:53:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 18758, "name": "设计感"}], "category": 3, "column": 33, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 192, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606154518fS8lIVKn7qTMLCze.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>1.黑，白，灰。</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154510ufDcrnpOgUAsaKNY.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>2. 或者马卡龙。巴黎马卡龙。</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154511tEuXfrl9ZmHe0RpA.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.796875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>3. 线条或几何的排列。</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154512wMdTOv07HVJiCfkq.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.68961625\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>4. 圆圈的集合效应。</strong><strong> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154512cFgjhOpxlD9t5Zd8.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.74662513\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>5. 木头。</strong><strong> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154513nm2LD0Yq4fSjl68V.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>6. 露天。</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154513cI9CVPX5slRBbzU6.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>7. 不规则地堆在一起。</strong><strong> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154514354ZkA6bMSPvEdy1.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.7109375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong>8. “素”。</strong></strong><strong><strong> </strong></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144626sDmGpfu5I0RKSrE9.gif\" width=\"1000\" height=\"825\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.825\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>9.</strong><strong>“仙”。</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154514bVvX4Oa1TSyDfKm6.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.86125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><span></span> </strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>10. 有一个词叫扁平。</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154515LAbYCskxgljVvENJ.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>11. 有一些用画的。</strong><strong> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154515ZrweBcRSIgVHoDFM.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>12. 变形的动物。 </strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061545160A3XHfeUYE4jOC9D.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>13.  动物的局部。</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154516YQVsp4L3yFnOCDa6.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.00733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong>14. 性别。</strong></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144628TwjWc8D7hLPQ3g6E.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"543\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.50277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>15. 不完整。也不要对称。</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154516USKqvwCsA2beJBuh.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>16. 或者，有对称的执念。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154517OBYNzEfDQ8wthaLK.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>17. 非传统</strong><strong> </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154518JRMYUf4SKQjV7pnh.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.74860335\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>18. 贵。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144629pRDYZXore7jyVSag.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"422\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.659375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>19. 能看脸。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144629UmnV3jDBSEbYKwkX.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong><strong></strong></strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><span style=\"text-align:left;\"><em></em></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><em><strong><strong></strong></strong></em></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><em><strong><strong><span style=\"text-align:left;\"><em></em></span></strong></strong></em></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><em>好奇心研究所的微博（</em><a href=\"http://weibo.com/p/1006065587974982/home?from=page_100606&amp;mod=TAB#place\" target=\"_blank\"><em>@好奇心研究所</em></a><span style=\"text-align:left;\"><em>）和微信公众号（ID：</em></span><span style=\"text-align:left;\"><em>QLab42</em></span><span style=\"text-align:left;\"><em>）全面上线啦，微信直接搜索「好奇心研究所」就可以订阅，关注与所长亲密接触，赶紧的。</em></span> </strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><span style=\"text-align:left;\"><em></em></span> </strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><em><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144631pVPZ6C5AswITHFOj.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"226\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.452\" data-format=\"gif\"></em> </strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n"}